verbose_text: Finally, the m 7 GTP pull-down assay showed that a significantly lower amount of eIF4E-7A but a significantly higher amount of eIF4E4-7E than wild-type eIF4E4 were pulled down (XREF_FIG), further demonstrating that the association of eIF4E4 with the m 7 G cap is strengthened by CRK1 mediated phosphorylation.
